&lt;/section&gt;&lt;h2 id="national-statistics"&gt;National statistics&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;All of the statistics published in this series are Official Statistics. The Department’s view is that all statistics which are not designated as National Statistics are robust and have been produced to a suitable standard.&lt;/p&gt;

