&lt;h2 id="national-statistics"&gt;National statistics&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Statistics from the National Travel Survey were assessed during 2010 by the UK Statistics Authority. An assessment report was published in October 2010. The statistics were confirmed as National Statistics in July 2011.&lt;/p&gt;

