&lt;/section&gt;&lt;p&gt;Older factsheets are available on request from the contact points below.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id="future-developments"&gt;Future developments&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The DfT ran a public consultation, on the future design of the National Travel Survey from June to September 2011. The consultation sought users’ views on the design of the NTS from 2013 onwards. The consultation document put forward a number of proposals to develop the NTS while reducing data collection costs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;A report containing a summary of responses to the consultation and details of the decisions the Department have made regarding the design of the survey from 2013 was published on 19 January 2012 and is available for download:&lt;/p&gt;

