&lt;/section&gt;&lt;h2 id="national-statistics"&gt;National statistics&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;National and regional figures related to this series are National Statistics. These statistics are currently being assessed by the United Kingdom Statistics Authority (UKSA) to determine their compliance with the Code of Practice for Official Statistics. An assessment report was published in June 2012 (Report 221).&lt;/p&gt;

